 Sixshooter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Japanese Sixshooter</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emotes</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick Draw</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gun Trick2</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324640/extras/e073d5b58bce04c6b89257a99b7f543b.webp?t=1731603463\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324640/extras/e073d5b58bce04c6b89257a99b7f543b.poster.avif?t=1731603463\" class=\"bb_img\" width=195 height=244 /></picture></span></p>",
